How about make it such that as they advance in level they can shape-shift
into a wider variety of other characters?
And make the length of the shift dependant on the level of the players
character, the character it&#39;s shifting to and maybe how much magical energy
it has - so more energy when cast = longer shift?.

It should also level at the slowest rate of all other characters to stop
people playing as the shifter, leveling faster, then constantly shifting
into say, a high-powered mage.

What do you think?

